Agadhi Churna - Phase 1 Implementation Plan (MVP)

Project Theme

Use the existing herbal branding throughout the website.

Color Palette

* Primary: Dark Forest Green #2F4F1E
* Secondary: Olive Green #6B7256
* Accent: Light Sage Green #E1E4DF
* Background: Pure White #FEFEFE
* Cards: Soft White #F6F6F5
* Text: Charcoal Black #111614

Design style should be modern, clean, premium, and healthcare-focused.

⸻

Phase 1 Goal

Deploy a working website today.

Instead of online payment, customers will place orders through WhatsApp.

⸻

User Authentication

Login

* Email
* Password
* Forgot Password
* JWT Authentication
* Session expires after 2 days

Signup

Fields:

* Full Name
* Email
* Mobile Number
* Password
* Confirm Password

Validation

* Email must be unique
* Mobile number must be unique
* Mobile number must contain exactly 10 digits
* Password confirmation required

⸻

Website Pages

1. Login Page

* Company Logo
* Login Form
* Forgot Password
* Create Account

⸻

2. Signup Page

* User Registration
* Validation Messages
* Success Message
* Redirect to Login

⸻

3. Home Page

Hero Section

* Product Banner
* Buy Now Button
* Call Now Button

About Section

About Agadhi Churna

Benefits Section

Weight gain benefits

Product Section

Since there are only a few products, no separate Products page is required.

Each product card contains

* Image
* Name
* Short Description
* Price
* Buy Now

Customer Reviews

Static review cards

Contact Section

* WhatsApp
* Call
* Address

Footer

* About
* Contact
* Social Links
* Copyright

⸻

Product Ordering Flow

Step 1

User clicks

Buy Now

↓

Open Order Form

⸻

Step 2

Customer fills

Personal Details

* Name
* Mobile Number
* Alternate Mobile (Optional)
* Email

Shipping Address

* Address
* Landmark
* District (Dropdown)
* State (Kerala)
* Country (India)
* PIN Code

Validation

* Phone = 10 digits
* Alternate Phone = 10 digits
* PIN Code = 6 digits
* Required fields cannot be empty

⸻

Step 3

Product Information

* Product Name
* Quantity (+ / −)
* Total Price

⸻

Step 4

Click

Send Order

Instead of payment,

Automatically open WhatsApp with a pre-filled message containing:

* Customer Name
* Phone
* Address
* District
* PIN Code
* Product Name
* Quantity
* Total Amount

This message is sent to the owner’s WhatsApp number.

⸻

Call Button

A floating Call Now button should directly dial the owner’s phone number.

⸻

Admin Panel

Dashboard

Overview cards

* Total Users
* Total Products
* Total Orders

⸻

